                  <additions ana="medium">
                     <p>Several comments added to poems in the margin</p>
                     <p>Pieces of Þóris þáttur hasts (1 folio), Hálfs saga og Hálfsrekka (5 folios),
                        Hrólfs saga kraka (1 folio) and a fragment of hátíðabænir (4 folios) are
                        kept with the manuscript (see item 7-10). A typed note on a slip of paper
                        inserted at the back: <q> Til Landsbókasafns. Meðfylgjandi handrit mun hafa
                           verið í eigu <name key="ThuLan001" type="person" role="owner">Þuríðar
                              Lange</name>, líklegast úr eigu föður hennar Jóels á Spákonufelli á
                           Skagaströnd. <name key="ThoMag017" type="person" role="scholar">Þór
                              Magnússon</name>. Kom <date>23/12 '77</date>. </q></p>
                     <p>The name of <name key="PalTom001" type="person" role="owner">Séra Páll Tómasson</name> á
                        <placeName>Knappsstöðum í Stíflu</placeName> can be found on fols. <locus from="1r" facs="#Lbs04-4827-0001r" to="1r">1r</locus>, <locus from="24v" facs="#Lbs04-4827-0024v" to="24v">24v</locus>, <locus from="62v" facs="#Lbs04-4827-0062v" to="62v">62v</locus>, <locus from="90v" facs="#Lbs04-4827-0090v" to="90v">90v</locus> and possibly on the verso side of the front fly leaf.</p>
                  </additions>
